<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://gohugo.io/" version="0.82.0">Hugo</generator><title type="html">toot on Sebastian Hoß</title><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/toot/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="HTML"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/toot/index.xml" rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="RSS"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/toot/atom.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" title="Atom"/><updated>2021-04-19T02:41:01+00:00</updated><id>https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/toot/</id><entry><title type="html">Send toots with GitHub Actions</title><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/send-toots-with-github-actions/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/send-emails-with-github-actions/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="related" type="text/html" title="Send emails with GitHub Actions"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/upload-release-assets-with-github-actions/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="related" type="text/html" title="Upload release assets with GitHub Actions"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/create-github-releases-with-github-actions/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="related" type="text/html" title="Create GitHub releases with GitHub Actions"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/publish-hugo-site-with-github-actions/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="related" type="text/html" title="Publish Hugo site with GitHub Actions"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/cache-maven-artifacts-with-github-actions/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="related" type="text/html" title="Cache Maven artifacts with GitHub Actions"/><id>https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/send-toots-with-github-actions/</id><published>2020-11-16T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2020-11-16T00:00:00+00:00</updated><content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The <a href="https://github.com/rzr/fediverse-action">rzr/fediverse-action</a> action allows to send a <a href="https://joinmastodon.org/">toot</a> in your <a href="https://github.com/features/actions">GitHub Action</a>.</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="nt">name</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">&lt;NAME&gt;</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w"></span><span class="nt">jobs</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">build</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">runs-on</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">&lt;RUN_ON&gt;</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">steps</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w">      </span>- <span class="nt">name</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">Publish Toot</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">uses</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">rzr/fediverse-action@master</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w">        </span><span class="nt">with</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w">          </span><span class="nt">access-token</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">${{ secrets.MASTODON_TOKEN }}</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w">          </span><span class="nt">message</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">&lt;MESSAGE&gt;</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w">          </span><span class="nt">host</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="l">${{ secrets.MASTODON_SERVER }}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div><ul>
<li><code>&lt;PIPELINE&gt;</code>: The name of your pipeline.</li>
<li><code>&lt;RUN_ON&gt;</code>: The runner to use, see GitHub&rsquo;s own <a href="https://help.github.com/en/actions/reference/workflow-syntax-for-github-actions#jobsjob_idruns-on">documentation</a> for possible values.</li>
<li><code>&lt;MESSAGE&gt;</code>: Message for the toot.</li>
</ul>
]]></content><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/categories/devops" term="devops" label="devops"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/categories/snippet" term="snippet" label="snippet"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/github" term="github" label="github"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/github-actions" term="github-actions" label="github actions"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/toot" term="toot" label="toot"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/mastodon" term="mastodon" label="mastodon"/></entry></feed>